    "7308314": {
        "Desc": "Light the Primal Torches",
        "Step": "New guidance has appeared on the Scarlet Sand Slate. Continue investigating based on the emerged words.",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Hulwani",
                    "T": "No, I refuse to escort you into the desert."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "But the Mausoleum of King Deshret, which has remained the same for centuries, has undergone an unprecedented change. You saw it too just now, didn't you? I need to make a record..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hulwani",
                    "T": "It's also my first time seeing this change... However, the sage has prohibited researchers from entering the desert without his permission."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "I—I'm not like those rash young researchers. I've dedicated years to studying in the Akademiya..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hulwani",
                    "T": "The answer is still \"no.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hello, long time no see. Seems like you're having a nice time in Aaru Village!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "Huh? What are the two of you doing here? I did say that I wouldn't pursue the matter, but you should stop going around deceiving people."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "I'm getting old, so my time is way more precious than yours. Besides, I have more important business to attend to. So, if you would excuse me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Wanna enter the desert?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Wanna get closer to the Mausoleum of King Deshret?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "No! Not at all! I would never go against the sage's restrictions! I just want to..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "Wait a minute, both of you are all covered in dirt, and you're holding a suspicious stone slate... Did you just return from the desert, by any chance?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "Are the... changes in the Mausoleum of King Deshret... linked to you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Yes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "How can that be? Generations of Vahumana researchers tried everything they could to open the mausoleum's entrance and discover the secrets within, yet none succeeded. But you two easily..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "Can I take a look at the stone slate you brought back with you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Sure."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "Thank you. The forest will remember your generosity!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "No, we're frauds."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "Hah! I knew it! Wait... Wh—where did you get this stone slate from?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Soheil's eyes open wide as he scans the stone slate from every angle. Even his breathing and speech speed up slightly."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "Due to various reasons, practically all the records of the later period of Al-Ahmar's civilization have been lost. Even those that are occasionally dug up are just fragments. I've never seen such a perfect stone slate!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "No, it's not only me. Even the sage may have never witnessed such a... miracle."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmph! You were calling us frauds just a short while ago!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "Did you really enter the Mausoleum of King Deshret as Tirzad's paper described?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Yep."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "I—It really is true then..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "In the name of Vahumana researcher Soheil and on behalf of my family, I sincerely apologize. I hope you'll be so kind as to forgive my greatest mistake — ignorance."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "No, he's a fraud."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "Please stop joking. I've always thought highly of Tirzad and considered him the future of Vahumana. I'm not in the least surprised that he wrote such a wonderful paper."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "Besides, he received a \"gift from the desert\" — the assistance of an outstanding traveler like you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "(Whoa, what a sudden change of attitude! It's like he's taken on a completely different character, just like the storytellers of Liyue do.)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "Could you... allow me to carefully inspect that stone slate? I'll compensate both of you for it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "As for the amount... Hmm... Before that, let's go someplace quiet so I can take a closer look at that slate."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
