    "7311001": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "Phew, it's a lot cooler here. Mind letting me see the slate?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Soheil examines the slate, alternating between frowning and marveling."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, you're spending too much time on this! You're not trying to commit the text to memory and skimp on our pay, are you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "Sorry, I was just so fascinated. This is my first time seeing writing like this..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Any discoveries?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "Hmm... Some of it looks like a construction log... It mentions \"Aaru,\" but there's no way to know if it's in any way connected to Aaru Village. Too bad the records say little more..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "But this discovery is certainly worth several pages of writing. Thank you very much. Here, as per our agreement."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You're welcome."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You should be thanking Tirzad instead."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That's right! If we weren't trying to prove Tirzad correct, we wouldn't have found this slate!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "You're right. Tirzad's the one I should be thanking — yes, indeed!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "My next step would be to find a bigger collection of primary materials, but that's going to be difficult without going into the desert..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "Oh, I have an idea! If you have the time, please hear me out..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hulwani",
                    "T": "Mr. Soheil, are you thinking..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hulwani",
                    "T": "The sage prohibits any researcher from going into the desert."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "Now, I wouldn't dare challenge the sage's authority, but I'm sure he never prohibited the giving of gifts, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Gifts? What are you going to give us?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "Something very precious... My archaeology notes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "To be honest, I ventured into the desert more than a dozen years ago, but didn't find anything special other than noting the locations of several potential ruins."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "I believe it's fate that brought me back here to make your acquaintance in these ruins, so I want you to have these notes!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hulwani",
                    "T": "Are you trying to... I get it. That isn't against the rules, but I'm afraid your actions would..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "#My actions? I am simply presenting a gift as a celebration of my friendship with {NICKNAME} the big hero and Paimon the little hero. Isn't that more than fair?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hulwani",
                    "T": "I suppose..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's fair indeed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's not very fair..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "Oh... Is it not enough? Well, consider it as a greeting gift. I'll have better ones for you later!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon thinks it's pretty fair..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Soheil",
                    "T": "Well, the little hero certainly thinks so. What does the big hero think?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Okay..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "The world of researchers is way too complicated! He could just have come right out and said he needed our help! Instead, we had to go through this whole charade..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "If you ask Paimon, he's just afraid that the big guy over there would rat him out to the sage."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's because your world is too simple, Paimon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Is it? Paimon thinks her world's pretty complicated. Paimon has to remember what every dish tastes like, and all the ways to get different treasures..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Wow, Paimon! You actually understood!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Of course! He was just short of writing \"Help me!\" all over his face! Hmm, if we help him now, I'm sure we'll get loads of rewards."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "He must have his reasons."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "True, but Paimon feels these researchers always hide behind the pretense of \"pursuing knowledge\"..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "As if that justifies everything they do and say."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Well, that's one thing you shouldn't turn into, Paimon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Don't worry, Paimon's never been interested in knowledge at all!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Let's take a look at what's written in Soheil's gift!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Mm... Looks like he's been having a pretty hard time. He explored the area around the Mausoleum of King Deshret for a month without obtaining any results. He didn't want to give up, and found the Transparent Ruins."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And then he found something a lot smaller than the Mausoleum of King Deshret — the Tomb of Carouses. Finally, he was attacked by a group of mercenaries in a place called Lamb-Devourer Rock."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whoa... Even though he went through all that, he still wrote that \"compared to the mockery, having no improvement in knowledge is more painful to endure.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "He sounded like a completely different person."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah! Seems like he really was in it for the knowledge back then. Paimon's a little moved."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "From that perspective, it wouldn't be an exaggeration for him to call this a precious gift."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Let's visit each location mentioned in his notes. If we find something decent, let's bring it back as a gift to him in return!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
